*event_2
;[exp] true

@se f=roar
@wait time=1000
[texton]
[？？？]「I won't give you the magic stone...」[k]
[textoff]
@se f=roar
@fg c=dragon_red left=450 top=-90
@w05
[texton]
Along with an eerie, resonant voice, a bright red dragon appeared before me![k]
[name n="Fire Dragon" f=dragon_01]「I will never hand over the Sapphire Magic Stone... The magic stone of ice is the most troublesome thing for us beings of fire...
 [k]
[name n="Fire Dragon" f=dragon_01]「That is why I buried the magic stone beneath this scorching lava... so that its power would never be wielded again.」[k]
[name n="Fire Dragon" f=dragon_01]「Adventurers... Perish here by my flames...!」[k]
[textoff]
@clf
@monster pos=3 name=ファイアドラゴン
@callbattle bgm=dragon gameover=true escape=false

@delevent
@flash on=1000
@eval exp='game.map.effect = void'
@eval exp='game.map.roof = "stone"'
@eval exp='tf.temp = %[type: "floor", img: "soild", trap: void]'
@eval exp='game.map.changeFloorsOfWideArea(tf.temp, 2, 3, 14, 11)'
@changefloor x=12 y=9 img=soil
@changefloor x=8 y=4 img=soilr
@changefloor x=8 y=3 img=soilr
@flash off=1000
@wait time=1000
[texton]
When we defeated the Fire Dragon, the lava that spread out before our eyes disappeared![k]
[textoff]

[eventoff]
